## 2026-03-27 - CommandPalette: No "Copy token value" action for token search results
- Added a "Val" button to each token row in the command palette token search mode (">"). Clicking it copies the raw token value to the clipboard. Added `value?: string` to `TokenEntry`, `onCopyTokenValue` prop to `CommandPalette`, included `value` in `paletteTokens` (serialized via `JSON.stringify` for non-string values), and wired the handler in App.tsx. The "Val" button appears before the "CSS" button in each row.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/CommandPalette.tsx` ~L57, ~L282; `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/App.tsx` ~L1116, ~L2730
